The femmes were around looking curious what was going there, suddenly 
Darkfate looked the computer that was in his wrist. and suddenly 
said "Aelo, take a shuttle and go to this coordinates"

"Yes sir!" said the femme

She leave the place and took a shuttle. Soon she was leaving the base 
and drove towards Greven's location.

"Here's Aelo" said the femme in Greven's frecuency "Don't worry, 
we're on the way... What's the situation there???"
